title: BIGNPC
content:
local Players = game:GetService("Players")
local npc = workspace:WaitForChild("Rig") -- pastikan namanya sama persis
local humanoid = npc:WaitForChild("Humanoid")

local function setScale(h, s)
	local function set(name, val)
		local v = h:FindFirstChild(name) or Instance.new("NumberValue", h)
		v.Name = name
		v.Value = val
	end
	set("BodyHeightScale", s) -- disini bisa ganti ukurannya
	set("BodyWidthScale", s)
	set("BodyDepthScale", s)
	set("HeadScale", s)
end

local function mirrorPlayer(plr)
	local ok, desc = pcall(function()
		return Players:GetHumanoidDescriptionFromUserId(plr.UserId)
	end)
	if ok and desc then
		humanoid:ApplyDescription(desc) -- ganti tampilan
		setScale(humanoid, 3)           -- tetap besar
	else
		warn("Gagal ambil description untuk", plr.Name)
	end
end

Players.PlayerAdded:Connect(function(plr)
	mirrorPlayer(plr)
end)

-- kalau main solo test sudah ada player:
for _,plr in ipairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do
	mirrorPlayer(plr)
end
